window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I'll never let him catch me</b></p> <p>The King of the North Pole was supposed to be an ally. He wasn't supposed to burn my kingdom in the South Pole to the ground and destroy everything I knew and loved. As the new Queen, I'll take my revenge no matter what it costs me.</p> <p>But Nicholas, the immortal Saint, is far more powerful than I ever imagined. And when he flips the script on my assassination attempt, I find myself running through a frosty woods, trying to outrun and outsmart the vicious and brutal ruler.</p> <p>Three Days. If I can evade him for just three days, he promises he'll let me go. But if he catches me before midnight on Christmas day, then the only gift I'll be finding under the tree is my worst nightmare: a wedding dress.</p> <p><i>Hunted in Holly</i> is a Dark Romance Christmas novella that takes a spicy holiday twist on <i>The Most Dangerous Game</i>. This high stakes game of Cat and Mouse will keep you as on edge as our heroine, with magic and heat amidst the twisted romance. You'll love it if you prefer your enemies to lovers romance with an immortal, morally gray love interest who loves the primal chase of his very, very \"good girl.\"</p>"; 
